Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.31,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs70\fnFZLanTingHei-B-GBK\shad3\4c&HA8AEB5&\pos(549.333,536)\fad(0,700)}準決賽
